ist.com/2014/08/nick-dominelli-seeks-office-in-york-south-weston/|title=Nick Dominelli Seeks Office in York-South Weston|last=Torontoist|date=2014-08-28|work=Torontoist|access-date=2017-04-19|language=en-US}}</ref> Endorsed by the [[Toronto Star]].<ref name=\":5\" />\n|-\n| Lekan Olawoye|| 3,441 ||20.84\n|02-Jan-14\n|Executive director of For Youth Initiative.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://torontoist.com/2014/09/lekan-olawoye-makes-council-bid-in-york-south-weston/|title=Lekan Olawoye Makes Council Bid in York-South Weston {{!}} politics {{!}} Torontoist|last=Torontoist|date=2014-09-02|language=en-US|access-date=2016-09-22}}</ref> Campaign issues included unemployment, affordable housing, and community safety.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.insidetoronto.com/news-story/4803899-lekan-olawoye/|title=Lekan Olawoye|last=InsideToronto.com|website=www.insidetoronto.com|access-date=2017-04-19}}</ref> Endorsed by [[Now (newspaper)|Now Magazine]]<ref name=\":6\" /> and [[Toronto & York Region Labour Council]].<ref name=\":8\" /> \n|-\n! Total|| 16,513 ||100\n!\n!\n|}\n\n===Ward 13 - Parkdale\u2014High Park===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 150px;\" | Candidate Name\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 100px;\" | Number of votes\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 100px;\" | % of votes\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 100px;\" | Nomination Date\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 500px;\" | Biography and policies\n|-\n| '''[[Sarah Doucette]]'''|| 16,202 ||65.62\n|13-Jan-14\n|Incumbent of Toronto City Council since 2010.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www1.toronto.ca/wps/portal/contentonly?vgnextoid=6b693293dc3ef310VgnVCM10000071d60f89RCRD&vgnextchannel=c3a83293dc3ef310VgnVCM10000071d60f89RCRD|title=Councillor Sarah Doucette - Council Members - Council Members {{!}} City of Toronto|language=en-CA|access-date=2017-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420045529/http://www1.toronto.ca/wps/portal/contentonly?vgnextoid=6b693293dc3ef310VgnVCM10000071d60f89RCRD&vgn